---
// src/components/blog/BlogCTA.astro
---
<div class="bg-brand-navy text-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 my-12 text-center shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-gold rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 transform translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-green rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 transform -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/2"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Need Personalized Support for Your Child?</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8 text-lg">
      Every child is unique. If you're looking for tailored strategies, developmental guidance, or a deeper understanding of your child's needs, we are here to help.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="https://calendar.app.google/zMKejpnpCjh91WRG7" class="bg-brand-gold text-brand-navy font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg transition-all text-center">
        Book a Consultation
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors text-center">
        Explore Services
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
      Available for families globally via online consultation. Local assessment available in Lahore, Pakistan.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
